title: Zhou Jieqiong, Eunwoo, And Yebin To Miss High School Graduation To Focus On Pristin’s Debut
text:
Pin   
On February 6, Pledis Entertainment said that Pristin’s Zhou Jieqiong, formerly a member of I.O.I, will not be attending her high school graduation ceremony. She has been attending School of Performing Arts Seoul (SOPA), along with her fellow members Eunwoo and Yebin, who had also been contestants of “Produce 101.” 
The agency added, “It is not just Zhou Jieqiong, Jung Eunwoo and Kang Yebin will also not be attending the graduation as they are in the midst of preparing for their debut.” 
Meanwhile, a number of idols who are also graduating from the school will be attending the ceremony, which will be held on February 7. They include GFRIEND’s SinB and Umji, Cosmic Girls’ Eunseo, BTS’s Jungkook, MOMOLAND’s Nayun, CLC’s Yeeun, Berry Good’s Daye, Sehyung, and Gowoon, and PENTAGON’s Jung Wooseok.
